Repository Structure
TITANIUM-4-IDS/
|-- README.md                    # This file
|-- LICENSE                      # MIT License
|-- requirements.txt             # Python dependencies
|-- .gitignore                   # Git exclusions
|-- src/
|   |-- IDSmodel.py             # Main inference pipeline
|   |-- utils.py                # Preprocessing utilities
|   |-- train_gatekeeper.py     # Layer 2 training
|   |-- train_forensics.py      # Layer 3 training
|   |-- train_sentinel.py       # Layer 4 training
|   |-- livetest.py             # Live traffic evaluation
|-- models/                      # Trained models (see Releases)
|-- notebooks/
|   |-- TITANIUM4_Training.ipynb
|   |-- TITANIUM4_LiveTest.ipynb
|-- data/                        # Dataset directory (user-provided)
|-- results/                     # Output directory
Trained Models
Pre-trained models are available in Releases:
Model	File	Size
L2 Gatekeeper	l2_gatekeeper.pkl	~2 MB
L3 Forensics	l3_forensics.pkl	~8 MB
L4 Sentinel	l4_sentinel.pkl	~45 MB
RobustScaler	scaler.pkl	~1 MB
Isotonic Calibrator	isotonic_calibrator.pkl	~1 MB
